(40, 24, 44, 40, 24, 42, 42, NULL, 'Readiness for the Lord''s Coming', 'Both passages emphasize the need for vigilance and readiness for the unexpected arrival of the Lord. The phrases ''be ye also ready'' and ''watch therefore'' highlight the importance of being prepared at all times.', 'theme', 0.426, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(40, 24, 44, 42, 12, 40, 40, NULL, 'Readiness for the Son of Man', 'Both passages emphasize the need for readiness as the Son of Man will come unexpectedly. The phrasing about coming ''at an hour when ye think not'' is a direct parallel, reinforcing the theme of vigilance.', 'parallel', 0.412, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
